---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTASection from "@components/CTASection.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Safety and Practical Info | Your Mali Guides" description="Practical safety-first guidance for planning Mali and West Africa routes with Djibril Kassogue.">
  <section class="section-pad bg-cream">
    <div class="container-site max-w-4xl">
      <p class="eyebrow">Safety and practical info</p>
      <h1 class="display-title mt-4 text-5xl text-indigo-deep md:text-7xl">Plan routes according to current conditions.</h1>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-700">
        <p>Djibril can advise on practical route planning, transport, timing, and safety considerations. Access to some regions can change, so every route should be checked close to travel dates.</p>
        <p>Always check current travel advisories and entry requirements before booking international travel. No route is described as risk-free or guaranteed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <CTASection title="Ask what is feasible now." text="Send your route idea to Djibril and ask what is realistic under current local conditions." />
</BaseLayout>
